reviewText: Picked up the Thai import that plays all regions! Love the campiness! Katie Savoy is awesome, along with Carridine and Hillis! You can't take this movie seriously, but it's a hellova lot of fun! Conan O' Brien is brilliantly hilarious! A must see! If you love goofy monster movies, you'll dig this!
It is interesting. I hope there'll be a (Region 1) DVD of it so I can see it.
